	"faq_car_door_number_q": "What is Car Number and Door Number?",
	"faq_car_door_number_a": "Each train car has its own ID in the format of a letter followed by 3 digits. Note that the same car numbers may appear in different trains on different lines.<br />Similarly, every door has its own ID in the format of U, D, A, or B followed by 1 digit.",
