	"faq_end_and_lcd": "Equipment Cabinets, Ceiling and LCD screens near train car joints",
	"faq_lcd_number_hint": "The numbers after the \"-\" character near the small LCD screens are not door numbers but screen numbers. However, the numbering logic is similar to door numbers, so you can still use it to identify your position.",
