	"faq_no_result_wrong_result_q": "No Results/Incorrect Results?",
	"faq_no_result_wrong_result_a": "The data source of this tool is not from officials, and train cars could be rearranged due to operation needs. Therefore, we cannot guarantee the accuracy of the data. If you have a result but it does not match your route, you can try clicking the \"Show Other Urban Lines\" (if available) button to show other lines' matching results."
